deco2800.arcade.model

Class Achievement

  • java.lang.Object
    • deco2800.arcade.model.Achievement

  • public class Achievement
extends java.lang.Object
    An immutable struct-like class used for storing information about an achievement. Note that while the fields are public, they're also final (to enforce immutability) which removes any invariant issues.
